docs/blog

# Secret / runtime-state hygiene — never bake credentials or data into an image.
# (COPY is already selective, but exclude these defensively so no stray copy or
# future `COPY .` can leak them. Keys live in the runtime /data/keys.env volume.)
**/.env
**/*.env
**/keys.env
**/secrets*
**/.secret*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/.netrc
**/auth.json
**/.api_keys*
data
/data
